00:03:38.990 --> 00:03:40.030
There are guesses.

00:03:40.030 --> 00:03:40.870
There's data.

00:03:40.870 --> 00:03:44.080
But the precise mechanism
is often not known.

00:03:44.080 --> 00:03:48.290
